{"tid":1686133,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"AMD RX5700 非公版 mech oc 刷成 5700xt mech oc","createTime":"2019-11-01T02:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T11:55:43.000Z","uid":46232,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"750717dfa3076a8b484e4c12e6a2336d46497d50","tid":1686133,"uid":46232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:49:20.000Z","msg":"事前聲明 刷BIOS 會令張卡失去官方保養 變磚 等風險<br />\n準備工功 download ATIFlash <a href=\"https://www.techpowerup.com/download/ati-atiflash/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techpowerup.com%2Fdownload%2Fati-atiflash%2F&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=5c9f8cab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.techpowerup.com/download/ati-atiflash/</a><br />\n搵你張卡的bios 文件 5700 &amp; 5700XT<br />\n受害者MSI RX5700 Mech OC 非公版 單bios 單8pin 供電 TDP 為75W+150W 共225W <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJLc8wh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJLc8wh.jpg&h=99b17085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.techpowerup.com/vgabios/?architecture=&amp;manufacturer=MSI&amp;model=RX+5700&amp;interface=&amp;memType=&amp;memSize=&amp;since=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techpowerup.com%2Fvgabios%2F%3Farchitecture%3D%26manufacturer%3DMSI%26model%3DRX%2B5700%26interface%3D%26memType%3D%26memSize%3D%26since%3D&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=0ab2817e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.techpowerup.com/vgabios/?architecture=&amp;manufacturer=MSI&amp;model=RX+5700&amp;interface=&amp;memType=&amp;memSize=&amp;since=</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktiFxS6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktiFxS6.jpg&h=8af3711e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相對應5700xt mech oc bios<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.techpowerup.com/vgabios/?architecture=&amp;manufacturer=MSI&amp;model=RX+5700+XT&amp;interface=&amp;memType=&amp;memSize=&amp;since=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techpowerup.com%2Fvgabios%2F%3Farchitecture%3D%26manufacturer%3DMSI%26model%3DRX%2B5700%2BXT%26interface%3D%26memType%3D%26memSize%3D%26since%3D&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=942b38a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.techpowerup.com/vgabios/?architecture=&amp;manufacturer=MSI&amp;model=RX+5700+XT&amp;interface=&amp;memType=&amp;memSize=&amp;since=</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6aQ8GM2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6aQ8GM2.jpg&h=74eba8b2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n把XT bios 改名為XT.rom放入ATIFlash dir <br />\n新增txt文 加入以下代碼<br />\n<em>@echo off<br />\ncls<br />\n<br />\necho Flashing card 0 with XT.rom...<br />\necho.<br />\namdvbflash -p 0 -f XT.rom<br />\necho.<br />\n<br />\npause</em><br />\n另存為flashxt.bat<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mTzpZAf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmTzpZAf.jpg&h=e6ae85d2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\ndouble click flashxt.bat <br />\n等佢刷完 reboot <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1qZ5J2x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1qZ5J2x.jpg&h=7d9e1430&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n成功的話 就變成一張2304 unit 的5700xt<br />\n<br />\n後話 刷完bios 個power limit 都仲係+20% <br />\n自動超頻到2130 入mhw 會hang driver<br />\n最終power limit 推到+10% 控制TDP為225W 上限以內 一小時mhw 後溫度表<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/93SCAb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93SCAb4.jpg&h=eca8e1e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea505201237b02cef902264309768a9b56cd84f3","tid":1686133,"uid":77771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:51:54.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢"},{"pid":"a43e5f2cd5ab9a4c7bd2c73ff0d20270e03b0e60","tid":1686133,"uid":3419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:53:00.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"fdded7ec2fd60122981346714603a56bbc611b6b","tid":1686133,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:53:25.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721,831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先40%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第二期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n民調眾籌LINK﹕<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=c01bcd2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"d691d894a6815e300a4dc1902ff0df36de6048b2","tid":1686133,"uid":239558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"勁，留個名先"},{"pid":"acc23684774a4788cf799abd78b553fc26bcc6e0","tid":1686133,"uid":77771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:59:06.000Z","msg":"仲有5700 XT power play mod 都好有趣"},{"pid":"82420ba4814e8bb311d312ec34bcd5ae3304f230","tid":1686133,"uid":46232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"後話2<br />\n攪完一輪 效能會有幾多提昇呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0EbsdjJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0EbsdjJ.png&h=29e26dba&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8AM7XM2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8AM7XM2.jpg&h=40413819&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n8600 分 過左2070頭 接近2060s <br />\n對比起公版5700 7800分 有近10% 提昇<br />\n以上分數只係參考 <a href=\"http://guru3d.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguru3d.com&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=c535fd1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">guru3d.com</a> 公版測試<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.guru3d.com/articles-pages/amd-radeon-rx-5700-and-5700-xt-review,26.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guru3d.com%2Farticles-pages%2Famd-radeon-rx-5700-and-5700-xt-review%2C26.html&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=dd0edf3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.guru3d.com/articles-pages/amd-radeon-rx-5700-and-5700-xt-review,26.html</a><br />\n另外一提 張卡最好有雙bios switch 刷死左都方便自己整 <br />\n單bios 刷不成功 可以用 雙gpu / gpu+igpu/apu 方法 刷番轉頭<br />\n供電為6+8pin 公版設計 理輪上可以輸入高達300W 就如同power play mod<br />\n比多D電 效能提昇更多 散熱最好自己改改佢"},{"pid":"29442c7d7a7a4f2f111ee9e5bca3fbe9372f3d23","tid":1686133,"uid":148413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:04:28.000Z","msg":"留名, 我有張公版RX5700都刷左RX 5700XT既bios，<br />\n張卡有改分體水冷，但係full load長期行都只可以行到1950 Mhz ~ 2000 Mhz, 行唔到2100Mhz, 會彈game"},{"pid":"c13782bbc2f87ae49b6cc7d5a787fab948b3fc3b","tid":1686133,"uid":77771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82420ba4814e8bb311d312ec34bcd5ae3304f230","tid":1686133,"uid":46232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"後話2<br />\n攪完一輪 效能會有幾多提昇呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0EbsdjJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0EbsdjJ.png&h=29e26dba&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8AM7XM2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8AM7XM2.jpg&h=40413819&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n8600 分 過左2070頭 接近2060s <br />\n對比起公版5700 7800分 有近10% 提昇<br />\n以上分數只係參考 <a href=\"http://guru3d.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguru3d.com&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=c535fd1c\" data-auto-link targ